{"type":"message","id":"c7a05e24","parentId":"9d48e922","timestamp":"2026-05-15T04:13:32.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Python isn't installed or not in PATH. Let me try a different approach. Let me use C# or just directly read the file with a more targeted approach. Actually, let me try to kill the background jobs first and use a simpler method.\n\nWait, looking back at the earlier output more carefully - I actually already found the key error:\n\n```\nFOUND_PATTERN [失败]:\n  构建失败 : System.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\n  构建失败 : System.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\n```\n\nSo the issue is \"存在差异资源包\" (there are differing asset bundles). This is the same YooAsset validation error as before.\n\nThe question is - did the pipeline retry after this error? Since the log shows Unity shutting down (the final lines show `Cleanup mono`, `debugger-agent: Unable to listen on 11772`), and no \"成功\" or \"完成\" message was found, the pipeline likely failed.\n\nBut wait - looking back at the broader search results more carefully:\n\n```\nFOUND_PATTERN [完成]:\n  Bundle文件加密完成：E:/Solo/nightoffullmoon/client/cardv/Bundles/Test1/StandaloneWindows64/DefaultPackage/OutputCache/defaultpackage_assets_artpackage_default_defaultresource_emptyprefab.bundle.encrypt\n  资源构建报告文件创建完成：E:/Solo/nightoffullmoon/client/cardv/Bundles/Test1/StandaloneWindows64/DefaultPackage/1.4.000/BuildReport_DefaultPackage_1.4.000.json\n```\n\nSo some build completion steps did happen - bundles were encrypted and build reports were created. But there was also a \"构建失败\" error. This suggests the pipeline might have had partial progress but ultimately failed on the YooAsset difference check.\n\nLet me check the bat exit process to see what actually happened. Let me look at the end of the log to check for more clues.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IIEbxCUfyjsSA8hVO0Cr1605","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"calm-s