{"type":"message","id":"15e7d68b","parentId":"24312516","timestamp":"2026-05-15T04:13:38.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This file is 375K lines, so Select-String is going to be slow again. Let me think of a smarter approach.\n\nSince I already know the line number where \"构建失败\" appears from the earlier analysis, let me try to directly read around those lines.\n\nActually, from the previous analysis I can see that \"构建失败\" appears twice. Let me try using .NET directly to find these lines quickly, or use a different strategy.\n\nLet me use `[System.IO.StreamReader]` which is much faster for searching.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_uedyBtPJtPM08ejicK9j0146","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_find_fast.ps1","content":"$path = \"E:\\Solo\\nightoffullmoon\\client\\cardv\\BuildPipeline_RunHotUpdate.log\"\n$reader = [System.IO.StreamReader]::new($path)\n$lineNum = 0\n$errorLines = @()\nwhile (($line = $reader.ReadLine()) -ne $null) {\n    $lineNum++\n    if ($line.Contains(\"构建失败\") -or $line.Contains(\"差异资源\") -or $line.Contains(\"存在差异\")) {\n        $errorLines += $lineNum\n    }\n}\n$reader.Close()\nWrite-Output \"Found at lines: $($errorLines -join ', ')\"\nWrite-Output \"Total lines: $lineNum\"\n\n# Now read surrounding context\nif ($errorLines.Count -gt 0) {\n    foreach ($errLine in $errorLines) {\n        $start = [Math]::Max(1, $errLine - 30)\n        $end = $errLine + 5\n        $content = [System.IO.File]::ReadAllLines($path)\n        Write-Output \"`n=== Context around line $errLine ===\"\n        for ($i = $start-1; $i -lt $end -and $i -lt $content.Length; $i++) {\n            Write-Output \"L$($i+1): $($content[$i])\"\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":71,"output":484,"cacheRead":32256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32811,"cost":{"input