{"type":"message","id":"feb7e0d0","parentId":"c8e46598","timestamp":"2026-05-15T04:14:29.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a much clearer picture. Let me summarize the key findings:\n\n1. **YooAsset build failed** - `IncrementalBuild pipeline build failed !` at line 374711\n2. **The error is**: `构建失败 : System.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！` This translates to \"Build failed: There are differing asset packages! Please check the warning message!\"\n3. **The specific differing bundles** are all in `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_*` - a bunch of UI view prefab bundles for the solo package.\n4. **However, the pipeline continued** after the build failure! Looking at the log, after the `IncrementalBuild pipeline build failed !` at line 374711, the pipeline continued executing:\n   - It went into `PipelineHotUpdate` (CDN update step)\n   - It went through `SetupLocalTestEnvironment`\n   - It went through `OrganizeConfigFolder`\n   - And then got to `- Completed reload, in 135.615 seconds`\n   \n5. **The pipeline kept running through the remaining steps** despite the build failure. The CDN upload steps (PipelineHotUpdate, SetupLocalTestEnvironment, OrganizeConfigFolder) all completed.\n6. The pipeline continued to Unity shutdown, with the final log lines showing `Cleanup mono`, `debugger-agent: Unable to listen on 11772`\n\nSo the pipeline **completed but with a failure** in the YooAsset build step. The subsequent steps (CDN upload, local test env setup) ran but might not have had the correct assets to work with since the build step failed.\n\nThe issue is the same as before: YooAsset is detecting differences between the newly built asset bundles and the previous ones, which causes the `TaskVerifyBuildResult` to fail. The specific differing bundles are all `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_*` bundles related to Solo package UI views.\n\nSince the batch file exited with code 0 but the pipeline reported build failure, I should report this to the main session.\n\nAlso, I should NOT send a message to the Feishu group announcing success since the build actually failed. I'll report the details to the main session.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我有了完整信息，让我清理临时文件并反馈结果。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_gGavTOg5fZoeG5bAZhQa8795","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"del \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_*.ps1\" \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_*.py\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":60097,"output":596,"cacheRead":36352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97045,"cost":{"input":0.00841358,"output":0.00016688,"cacheRead":0.001017856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009598315999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778818460295,"responseId":"51061216-aee3-4883-8933-7831dcd36d98"}}
