{"type":"message","id":"e001ae8b","parentId":"dc0b2b3e","timestamp":"2026-05-15T04:14:47.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me provide a comprehensive summary to the main session. The build failed due to YooAsset verification issues. I should NOT send a message to the Feishu group since the build failed (no point in telling 兵王 the update failed, and the main agent can decide what to do).\n\nLet me compose my final message that will be auto-reported to the main agent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"任务完成。以下是完整的反馈报告：\n\n---\n\n## 热更流水线执行报告 (重跑 v2)\n\n### 状态：❌ 构建失败\n\n**流水线进程已结束**，bat 返回码 0（PowerShell 正常退出），但 Unity 构建本身失败。\n\n### 错误详情\n\n**YooAsset 增量构建验证失败** - 与上次相同的错误：\n\n```\n构建失败 : System.Exception: 存在差异资源包！请查看警告信息！\nIncrementalBuild pipeline build failed !\nBuild task failed : TaskVerifyBuildResult\n```\n\n**差异资源包列表**（均为 Solo 包 UI 视图 prefab）：\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolomanualfilterpanel.bundle`\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolomanualmainpanel.bundle`\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolomanualsettingpanel.bundle`\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolomgrpanel.bundle`\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolomultiplebuypanel.bundle`\n- `solopackage_assets_artpackage_solo_prefab_ui_view_uisolopreformationitempanel.bundle`\n- + 更多 solo UI bundle ...（共约 20-30 个差异资源包，都是 `uisolo*panel` 相关）\n\n### 日志关键位置\n\n- 错误行：~line 374711 (`IncrementalBuild pipeline build failed !`)\n- 完整日志 375K 行，37MB，编码 GBK\n\n### 流水线执行情况\n\n1. ✅ Unity Editor 正常启动并打开项目\n2. ✅ Library import 完成（耗时 135 秒 reload）\n3. ❌ YooAsset 增量构建验证失败（`TaskVerifyBuildResult` 检测到差异资源包）\n4. ⏩ 后续 CDN 上传步骤（PipelineHotUpdate、SetupLocalTestEnvironment、OrganizeConfigFolder）**仍然执行了**，但资源构建步骤本身失败，上传的 CDN 数据可能不完整\n5. ✅ Unity 正常关闭\n\n**未在飞书群通知兵王**（构建失败，无需通知）。\n\n### 建议\n\n主人之前说已经检查过，但这个错误仍然存在。可能有以下原因：\n1. Solo 包的 UI prefab 资源被修改过，与 CDN 上已有版本不一致\n2. 需要手动在 Unity 中打开 BuildPipeline 窗口，检查 \"热更\" 流水线的配置，看是否需要切换到 **Full Build** 模式（跳过差异检测），或者清理之前的差异缓存\n3. 或者需要在 YooAsset 设置中清空之前的构建缓存再重试"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":32,"output":695,"cacheRead":98048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98775,"cost":{"input":0.00000448,"output":0.00019460000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002745344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0029444239999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778818479402,"responseId":"3819503d-3091-4e96-9311-836116e217aa"}}
